"title": "5511: safety",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5511",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Being free from danger or harm. God promises to keep his people from all lasting spiritual and physical danger; he requires, however, that his people act responsibly.</p>\n<h2>God promises safety</h2>\n<h3>To his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:10\">DEU 12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:12\">DEU 33:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:26-Deut33:29\">DEU 33:26–33:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:8\">PSA 48:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:37-Jer32:38\">JER 32:37–32:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:11\">ZEC 14:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:31\">ROM 8:31</a></p>\n<h3>To those who trust in him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:9-Ps91:10\">PSA 91:9–91:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:13-Job11:19\">JOB 11:13–11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:3\">PSA 37:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:10\">PRO 18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:25\">PRO 29:25</a></p>\n<h3>To those who obey him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:18-Lev25:19\">LEV 25:18–25:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:5\">LEV 26:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:33\">PRO 1:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:21-Prov3:26\">PRO 3:21–3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:26\">PRO 28:26</a></p>\n<h3>To those in need</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:11\">JOB 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:15\">JOB 5:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:30\">ISA 14:30</a></p>\n<h3>But not to the wicked</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:4\">JOB 5:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:18\">PRO 28:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:12\">JER 12:12</a></p>\n<h2>Safety from enemies</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:6\">HEB 13:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:21\">JOS 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:5-Ps3:6\">PSA 3:5–3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:7\">PSA 12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:20\">PSA 31:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:53\">PSA 78:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:26\">EZK 28:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:10\">REV 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Safety from dangers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:2\">ISA 43:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:4\">PSA 23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:25\">EZK 34:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:28\">EZK 34:28</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual safety</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:18\">1JN 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:35–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:18\">2TI 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:11\">REV 2:11</a></p>\n<h2>Safety in God alone</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:8\">PSA 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:10\">ZEC 8:10</a></p>\n<h3>Safety in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:12\">JHN 17:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:5-Jer23:6\">JER 23:5–23:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:15-Jer33:16\">JER 33:15–33:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:11-John10:15\">JHN 10:11–10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28-John10:30\">JHN 10:28–10:30</a></p>\n<h2>Angels providing safety</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:6\">MAT 4:6</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:10-Luke4:11\">LUK 4:10–4:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:16\">GEN 19:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:15-Gen48:16\">GEN 48:15–48:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:20\">EXO 23:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:11-Ps91:12\">PSA 91:11–91:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:28\">DAN 3:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:22\">DAN 6:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:19\">ACT 5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:11\">ACT 12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:2-Rev7:3\">REV 7:2–7:3</a></p>\n<h2>Human responsibility for safety</h2>\n<h3>Personal</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:15\">PRO 11:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:6\">JER 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:1\">JER 6:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:15-Matt24:16\">MAT 24:15–24:16</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:14\">MRK 13:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:20-Luke21:21\">LUK 21:20–21:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:40\">ACT 2:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:44\">ACT 27:44</a></p>\n<h3>Family</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:9\">GEN 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:9\">GEN 43:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen44:32\">GEN 44:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13\">MAT 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>Friends</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:12-1Sam20:13\">1SA 20:12–20:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:22-1Sam22:23\">1SA 22:22–22:23</a></p>\n<h3>Neighbours</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:5-Exod22:15\">EXO 22:5–22:15</a></p>\n<h3>Officials</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:7\">NEH 2:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:24\">ACT 23:24</a></p>\n<h3>Kings</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:25\">1KI 4:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:5\">2CH 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:15\">2CH 15:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:28\">PRO 20:28</a></p>\n<h3>Pastors</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:17\">HEB 13:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:11-John10:15\">JHN 10:11–10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:28\">ACT 20:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:1\">PHP 3:1</a></p>\n<h2>Concern for safety</h2>\n<h3>David for Absalom</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:29\">2SA 18:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:32\">2SA 18:32</a></p>\n<h3>Mephibosheth for David</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:24\">2SA 19:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:30\">2SA 19:30</a></p>\n<h3>Father for son</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:27\">LUK 15:27</a></p>\n<h2>Prayers for safety</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:1\">PSA 16:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:15\">EXO 33:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:21-Ezra8:23\">EZR 8:21–8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:15\">JOB 30:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:20\">JOB 30:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:8-Ps17:9\">PSA 17:8–17:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:13\">PSA 19:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4-Ps27:5\">PSA 27:4–27:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:29\">PSA 119:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:1-Ps140:4\">PSA 140:1–140:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:8-Ps141:10\">PSA 141:8–141:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a></p>\n<h2>Possible dangers inherent in safety</h2>\n<h3>False security</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:3\">1TH 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:19\">DEU 29:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:27-1Kgs22:28\">1KI 22:27–22:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:26-2Chr18:27\">2CH 18:26–18:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:9\">JOB 21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:16-Job21:18\">JOB 21:16–21:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:6\">EZK 39:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:25\">DAN 8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:3-Obad1:4\">OBA 1:3–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:15\">ZEP 2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Complacency</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:32\">PRO 1:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a></p>\n<h3>Wickedness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:9-Jer7:10\">JER 7:9–7:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:26\">EZK 39:26</a></p>\n<h2>Perfect safety in God's kingdom</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:6-Isa11:10\">ISA 11:6–11:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:4\">ISA 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:25\">ISA 65:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:18\">HOS 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:3-Mic4:4\">MIC 4:3–4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16\">REV 7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:10\">ISA 49:10</a></p>",
